        ],
        "content": [
            "王子一行与奈迪犹产生了激烈的冲突。\\n正当一行面对奈迪犹那无可匹敌的力量\\n陷入走投无路的境地之时，\\n奈迪犹却突发异常并痛苦地离去。\\n对此，王子一行决定追上去一探究竟。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "圣树·上层\\n云上巨枝",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "奈迪犹！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "别再碍我的事，尤蒂尔。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我……在了解到你的身世\\n和你的志向这一切之后，\\n依然无法认同你的做法。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100054_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "要是不阻止你，\\n就会出现许多受苦之人。\\n我不能眼睁睁地放你走。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "即使拼上性命，我也要阻止你！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "区区空壳也敢大言不惭……\\n有本事就试试。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "telop",
            "context": "\\n两位契约者\\nDragalia Lost ～失落的龙约～ 第22章\\n \\n ",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "如果创世的造物主\\n“起始之人”成功复活，\\n这个世界将不再有任何可能性。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "奈迪犹为了让世界\\n免受“起始之人”的影响\\n而一直渴望得到巴哈姆特的力量。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "尽管我能够理解他的理想，\\n但他所采取的方式\\n无疑会牺牲众多生命。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我不能对此熟视无睹。\\n无论如何都要阻止奈迪犹！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "二人",
            "context": "哈啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "本打算一招就结束这场战斗，\\n没想到你竟能撑到现在，\\n值得表扬。不过——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "唔……太强了……\\n明明拥有如此力量……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "却为何要……我不明白……\\n为什么！奈迪犹！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "什么为什么？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "你不仅有着如此强大的力量，\\n还有头脑，还有着坚定的理想和信念。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "芩罗达说过，\\n你曾身为弱者，\\n因此更能理解弱者的痛苦。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "那你又为什么要牺牲\\n那些无辜的人们！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "我说过，\\n华而不实的想法救不了任何人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "在你找到对抗“起始之人”的方法之前，\\n无论你说些什么，都没有任何意义。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "更何况，凭你那浅薄的思想，\\n怎么可能阻止得了我！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "哇啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01",
                "100006_01",
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "尤蒂尔！\\n我这就来帮你！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "来再多少人也改变不了结果！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伙伴们",
            "context": "哇啊啊啊啊！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "不行……与巴哈姆特缔结契约后\\n他的力量更加强大了……\\n这样下去我们无计可施……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100054_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "成功缔结契约的不只是奈迪犹。\\n用我的力量来阻止他！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100054_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "巴哈姆特！\\n请赐予我力量吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120245_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴哈姆特",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "呃！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "好机会！我们乘胜追击！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01",
                "100010_05",
                "100005_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "全员",
            "context": "哈啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "愚蠢。你们以为能赢得过我吗？\\n虽说是巴哈姆特，\\n这种半吊子的力量可奈何不了我！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "真是可悲啊，塞西娅。\\n强行缔结契约却无法“龙化”，\\n充其量也只能通过魔力进行复制。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100054_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "即使是半吊子……即使可悲……\\n我也会竭尽全力来阻止你！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "既然如此，我就让你\\n见识一下巴哈姆特真正的力量吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "创世之龙啊，赐予我契约之力吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01",
                "100054_01",
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "全员",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210162_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "亲身感受一下\\n创世之龙的力量吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100054_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "不好！\\n巴哈姆特，拜托你了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120245_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴哈姆特",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100054_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "嗯！？呀啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "全员",
            "context": "哇啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100054_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "唔唔……巴哈姆特……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210162_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "懂了吗，塞西娅。\\n你是无法自如使用巴哈姆特的力量的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210162_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "老老实实地把契约交给我。\\n这才是对抗“起始之人”的唯一手段。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100054_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "我做不到。\\n你的方法会使无数人因此牺牲，\\n我不可能对此熟视无睹……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210162_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "那你想要的结局\\n就是等“起始之人”毁掉所有\\n可能性之后再后悔吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210162_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "为什么你就是不明白\\n这种做法有多愚蠢！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "不！不明白的人是你，奈迪犹！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "寻找一个不用牺牲任何人的方法……\\n这种想法也许确实华而不实……\\n然而……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这种华而不实的想法，才正是可能性！\\n这正是所有可能性之中\\n最完美的选择。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "你明明想要保护可能性\\n不受“起始之人”破坏，\\n却又为什么要否定可能性！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "你又为什么就是不能明白\\n这其中的矛盾呢！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210162_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "区区躯壳，嘴炮倒是厉害……既然如此，\\n不如你让我见识一下你所谓的可能性？\\n让我看看你如何拯救这世界的可能性？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210162_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "可能性并不平等。\\n强者有权得到更多的选择，\\n弱者则会被剥夺选择的权利。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210162_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "如果你认为你的选择\\n能比我的方法带来更多的可能性，\\n那就在这里赢过我吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210162_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "否则，无论你说些什么，\\n都将是一纸空谈！\\n区区一副躯壳，赶快消失吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "唔……接下来这招\\n如果没办法处理的话，\\n我们都会没命……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "也就是说……我们走投无路了啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "唔！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210162_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "这下，\\n故事要结束了……嗯！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210162_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "唔啊啊啊……怎、怎么……回事！？\\n呃啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "怎、怎么回事……\\n他好像突然变得很痛苦！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_901"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "该死……\\n居然在这种时候……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_01_0064",
            "book_image": ""
